❯ advice or instructions on how to subscribe to payment services like stripe and paypal                                                                                                                    

⏺ Signing up for Stripe

  1. Go to stripe.com and click Start now — no business license required to open an account
  2. Enter your email, name, and password
  3. Verify your email
  4. Fill in your business profile: business type (you can select "Individual/Sole proprietor"), country, industry (Home Services), and your EIN or SSN
  5. Add a bank account so payouts deposit automatically
  6. Once approved you'll have access to the dashboard

  Keys you need for this site:
  - Dashboard → Developers → API keys
  - Copy the Publishable key (starts with pk_live_...) → goes in assets/js/payment.js
  - Copy the Secret key (starts with sk_live_...) → goes in Cloudflare Pages env vars as STRIPE_SECRET_KEY

  Stripe also gives you test keys (pk_test_... / sk_test_...) so you can run the full payment flow with fake card numbers before going live. Use those first.

